{"tid":522336,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【唔係C朗美斯】全球最有錢球員係...","createTime":"2018-01-07T12:39:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-07T13:30:27.000Z","uid":4661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ab77b1774886dddf40f33c6ec73e4bfe9f1a32ce","tid":522336,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T12:39:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180106/photo/bkn-20180106203324019-0106_00882_001_01p.jpg?20180107023953\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20180106%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180106203324019-0106_00882_001_01p.jpg%3F20180107023953&h=f31afaae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔少年輕人，新年願望都係希望不勞而獲，周時發夢都諗，點解自己唔係富二代？其實富二代都唔係個個係二世祖，包奇亞雖然未來有機會繼承150億鎊（！）遺產，但佢依然冇放棄足球夢，依家正效力李斯特城，希望未來可於球壇發光發熱。呢名19歲嘅汶萊國家隊隊長，佢舅父正正係汶萊蘇丹（元首），佢爸爸係汶萊皇室成員，一個月使費高達3500萬鎊，仲曾於包奇亞7歲時候，搵「流行音樂天王」米高積遜為其家族作私人表演，堅誇張。<br />\n<br />\n包奇亞98年於洛杉磯出世，好快就愛上足球，11歲開始加入修咸頓青年軍，之後去過阿仙奴同車路士試腳，最終舊年加入李斯特城簽約3年，依家踢緊狐狸後備隊。雖然仲未於英超搵到位置，但佢喺汶萊國家隊係舉足輕重人物，呢名翼鋒係國家隊隊長，可見有一定質素。包奇亞表示：「我識性之後就開始鍾意踢波，家人都好支持我。」據聞現時英冠一哥狼隊，有意斟包奇亞過檔，如果成事，下季包奇亞或有機會以正選球員身份亮相英超。<br />\n<br />\n包奇亞個舅父，係汶萊國家元首，於97年曾成為全球首富，包奇亞堅係衣食無憂，就算成世唔做嘢都冇問題。佢爸爸Jefri，係汶萊王室中著名花花公子，每月喺衣食及奢侈品上，閒閒哋花費3500萬鎊，名下共有2300部名車。於自己50歲生日會，佢為氹囝囝包奇亞，豪花1250萬鎊邀請米高積遜，去到汶萊為佢家族表演。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180106/photo/bkn-20180106203324019-0106_00882_001_02p.jpg?20180107023953\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20180106%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180106203324019-0106_00882_001_02p.jpg%3F20180107023953&h=ab045386&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180106/photo/bkn-20180106203324019-0106_00882_001_03p.jpg?20180107023953\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20180106%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180106203324019-0106_00882_001_03p.jpg%3F20180107023953&h=2a2136a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180106/photo/bkn-20180106203324019-0106_00882_001_05p.jpg?20180107023953\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20180106%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180106203324019-0106_00882_001_05p.jpg%3F20180107023953&h=9a1c64f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180106/photo/bkn-20180106203324019-0106_00882_001_06p.jpg?20180107023953\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20180106%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180106203324019-0106_00882_001_06p.jpg%3F20180107023953&h=c202cdd9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b8a8b26bf8604ce1664f4fba980d36c37a88874d","tid":522336,"uid":90766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T12:41:57.000Z","msg":"李城未來國王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5f1288e8b46abfade80f00d6187d8d7dba179ac","tid":522336,"uid":25754,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T13:02:49.000Z","msg":"失業漢法明尼排第幾?"},{"pid":"a8b0fd49db3ed9aaa1ee298682e5b72e4a2097ae","tid":522336,"uid":20747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5f1288e8b46abfade80f00d6187d8d7dba179ac","tid":522336,"uid":25754,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T13:02:49.000Z","msg":"失業漢法明尼排第幾?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T13:22:17.000Z","msg":"佢都應該先係第一<br />\n佢間公司世界無野取替到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f1e29f4565b3d80f978d1f6f94c270933e39c9f","tid":522336,"uid":40932,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T13:28:55.000Z","msg":"個國家隊隊長個位都唔會係用實力囉到掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9120944020f61a482f5823551346d8c0d1bd15c6","tid":